{"tid":2516169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤工強姦分居妻罪脫","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:28:10.000Z","uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe3f4fc273752ac27f0b1c82cec37522a63486e","tid":2516169,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"婚內強姦可以脫罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//地盤工人前年要求已分居的妻子復合，涉嫌以剪刀恐嚇並綁起妻子手腕進行強姦，地盤工否認刑事恐嚇及強姦兩罪，案件經過八日審訊，陪審團退庭商議近七小時後，以六比一大比數裁定刑事恐嚇罪名成立，一致裁定強姦罪脫。張慧玲法官考慮到被告拿起剪刀後「好快放返低」，終判其監禁兩年，而被告被捕後還押至今已超過兩年，故被告能當庭釋放。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A5%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E5%88%86%E5%B1%85%E5%A6%BB%E7%BD%AA%E8%84%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E7%8D%B2%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%AD%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE-091700738.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E8%2584%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-091700738.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK5S9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=771575f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A5%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E5%88%86%E5%B1%85%E5%A6%BB%E7%BD%AA%E8%84%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E7%8D%B2%E7%95%B